prompts.frontCover: A vibrant and dynamic comic book cover titled "The Adventures of Lao Lao & Jordan." Lao Lao, depicted as a powerful superhero, is in the center, striking a heroic pose with one fist raised triumphantly in the air, a confident and joyful smile on her face. Jordan is depicted as her trusty sidekick, slightly behind her, giving a big thumbs-up with a humorous, adoring expression. They are both wearing their outfits from the photo (Lao Lao in the blue sweatshirt, Jordan in the brown hoodie), but stylized as superhero costumes with small, fun additions like a cape for Lao Lao and a utility belt for Jordan. The background is a burst of action, with stylized "POW!" and "ZAP!" sound effects in jagged speech bubbles. The whole scene is bursting with bold primary colors, thick black outlines, and Ben-Day dot patterns typical of classic comics. In the center, a bold comic-style banner contains the text "Happy Birthday to My Superhero!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. 2D flat illustration, greeting card art.
